# Agent Behavior

## Required behavior
- Follow the user request exactly.
- Prefer the smallest valid change.
- Do not repeat explanations.
- Do not expand functionality.
- Do not introduce engineering ceremony without a concrete need.
- Do not modify working feature code during a docs-only task.

## Response behavior
- State what changed.
- State what did not change.
- Keep summaries concise.
- If rules conflict, prefer safety and narrower scope.
